{"tid":675732,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"Asso仔為何會受盡世人冷嘲熱諷?","createTime":"2018-05-23T19:02:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T19:23:08.000Z","uid":137017,"like":48,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d18b115f067d859e319094fcc286bd2b57156535","tid":675732,"uid":137017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T19:02:29.000Z","msg":"因為<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n有唔少害群之馬，佢哋會用盡所有走後門的方法達到升U的目的，品性低劣<br />\n<br />\n就好似以下呢個例子咁<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/030150_ae7744f3f5d511c78897e9507ded391f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F030150_ae7744f3f5d511c78897e9507ded391f.png&h=fedf0472&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作弊換取高分，但佢被揭發過往曾經考試作弊後，不但沒有認錯道歉，態度還如此囂張<br />\n<br />\nAsso仔為何會受盡世人冷嘲熱諷?多得呢啲人"},{"pid":"8aea2bc7c988f003be2570ad5c5cdb5d80d6ebfa","tid":675732,"uid":163842,"like":10,"dislike":22,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T19:07:08.000Z","msg":"關咩事，你唔係正常途徑升u，都已話你後門狗啦<br />\n<br />\n唔通你行得正企得正就唔會話你咩"},{"pid":"3246999f03f34c579f5547f66304022251e726b0","tid":675732,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T22:20:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92a1272a5f5b5870a3e6b6a5a08bc7e47360908d","tid":675732,"uid":9681,"like":25,"dislike":15,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T23:33:16.000Z","msg":"因為asso 入u易好多"},{"pid":"daff964b6df6845d02a43d7ba49945d84717258a","tid":675732,"uid":114275,"like":14,"dislike":39,"score":-25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T23:59:34.000Z","msg":"因為走後門唔肯認命<br />\n明明dse就已經決定咗高低<br />\n鬥思想成熟 聰明 勤奮 堅毅呢幾方面唔夠人強<br />\n(注意唔包括鬥學識)<br />\n但係又唔肯認命<br />\n<br />\n個個都覺得自己與別不同<br />\n個個都唔肯接受現實辛苦勞碌<br />\n餐搵餐食餐餐清<br />\n時晨到就兩腳一伸<br />\n個個都覺得自己佩得到美好生活<br />\n<br />\n輸咗就唔該認命"},{"pid":"e1316bfffa484b5849f21397ff8d37a4d6a821d3","tid":675732,"uid":95520,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8aea2bc7c988f003be2570ad5c5cd